/target
# Stray target dir from running cargo inside the workspace member directly.
/durare-macros/target/
# The benchmark harness is its own workspace with its own build dir.
/durare-benchmarks/target/
Cargo.lock
# ... but the benchmark harness is a binary: its lockfile is committed so a
# benchmarked dependency set is reproducible.
!/durare-benchmarks/Cargo.lock
**/*.rs.bk
.env
# Internal Go-parity development tracker; not for the public repo.
/PARITY.md
# Internal cross-SDK conformance tracker; not for the public repo.
/CONFORMANCE.md
/durare-benchmarks/cross/go/durare-bench-go
